text: haey yeung minban banhchoun anakneasar na mneak leukleng te tam pheasaea nei krom robsa ke bonnaoh daembi ponyol yeang chbasa dl puokke . haey a l laoh thveu aoy v nge v ng champoh anaknea del trong mean chetnea haey trong changaoulobangheanh champoh anaknea del trong mean chetnea . haey trong mha khlangpouke mha ktebandet
